Third Avenue, adjoining the N.E. corner of E. 188th Street. The old barn, in the center of the view, appears on Bromley's map as early as 1879.

E. 188th Street, east from Park Avenue to Third Avenue, showing the Third Avenue Elevated Line, on the latter thoroughfare.

title: Bronx: East 188th Street - East, Park to Third Avenues.
